//! Base library — Lua's built-in functions (`print`, `type`, `pairs`, `pcall`, …).
//!
//! Translated from: `reference/lua-5.4.7/src/lbaselib.c` (549 lines, 32 functions)
//! Target crate: `lua-stdlib`

